::Epyon::

He nods to Khonklor, anmd then follows Mantle through the shields.
"My team are bringing the parts over now."

::Hot Rod::

The flame forces him back. His movement allows Vehements shots to miss.
He continued to fire at Unicron, but ran around so Unicron didn't have a
good shot.

::DrillBit::

He jumps, only one shot hitting him in the leg. He again, openes
gattaling gun fire on Unitron.

::Dollon::

He is hit right in the head, and stumbles around dazed.
